Sprott Asset Management


Sprott Asset Management is one of the biggest asset management firms in Canada, as well as North America. The firm is headquartered at Toronto, Ontario. They cater to both individual and institutional clients and provide them with a number of asset management products and services. 










Sprott Asset Management was established in the month of August, 2000. Sprott Asset Management is a privately held company that deals in investment fund services. The ownership of the company is with its employees.
Sprott Asset Management aims at providing the maximum possible returns to its clients. It has been certified by the Investment Dealers Association. It is a member of the Canadian Investor Protection Fund, as well.
Sprott Asset Management obtained the membership of the Alternative Investment Management Association (AIMA) Canada in the year 2004. Services and Products of Sprott Asset Management
